Package: forge-dpu
Version: SED__DPU_AGENT_PKG_VERSION
Section: base
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Forge team <swngc-forge-dev@nvidia.com>
Description: Forge specific customizations for Bluefield-2 and future DPUs.
 Installs forge-dpu-agent, plus otelcol-contrib to export its logs and metrics.
 Includes an agent that copies the mTLS certs of forge-dpu-agent and renews
 them independently on the same schedule.
